PN,37301
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1777651868
OL,3,CMan returns medieval tiles after
OL,4,Ckeeping them in biscuit tin for 59
OL,5,Cyears
OL,7,FMark Gough was there as medieval tiles
OL,8,Fwere returned to their rightful spot
OL,9,Fafter 59 years in a biscuit tin
OL,11,FA man has returned medieval floor
OL,12,Ftiles to a Shropshire priory, almost
OL,13,Fsix decades after he took them as a
OL,14,F"keepsake."
OL,16,FSimon White, 68, a retired Chartered
OL,17,FSurveyor, was taken to visit heritage
OL,18,Fsites throughout the county as a young
OL,19,Fboy, and on one visit to Wenlock
OL,20,FPriory, his father encouraged him to
OL,21,Ftake some tiles as a family souvenir.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1777651868
OL,3,CMan returns medieval tiles after
OL,4,Ckeeping them in biscuit tin for 59
OL,5,Cyears
OL,7,FHe says he has felt "uneasy" about it
OL,8,Fever since, and was pleased to
OL,9,Frediscover them in a "battered"
OL,10,Fbiscuit tin while sorting through his
OL,11,Floft.
OL,13,FBut if it wasn't for his mother's
OL,14,Fdiaries, Simon said he would not have
OL,15,Fbeen able to remember where the tiles
OL,16,Fhad come from.
OL,18,F"Fortunately, my mother kept very
OL,19,Fdetailed diaries written in tiny,
OL,20,Fspindly handwriting," he said.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1777651868
OL,3,CMan returns medieval tiles after
OL,4,Ckeeping them in biscuit tin for 59
OL,5,Cyears
OL,7,F"I read them again and was able to
OL,8,Fpinpoint one summer's day in 1967 when
OL,9,Fwe came to Wenlock Priory and I
OL,10,Fthought it had to be the best bet."
OL,12,FAfter Simon contacted English
OL,13,FHeritage, the tiles were confirmed to
OL,14,Fbe missing pieces of the striking
OL,15,Fmedieval tiled floor at the priory in
OL,16,FMuch Wenlock, dating from the late
OL,17,F13th to early 14th century.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1777651868
OL,3,CMan returns medieval tiles after
OL,4,Ckeeping them in biscuit tin for 59
OL,5,Cyears
OL,7,FHeritage curator Matty Cambridge was
OL,8,F"delighted" to get Simon's email, and
OL,9,Fsaid the tiles are actually better
OL,10,Fpreserved than some of the ones which
OL,11,Fhave been exposed to the elements at
OL,12,Fthe priory.
OL,14,F"It's lovely to be able to hold them
OL,15,Fand really see just how detailed they
OL,16,Fare," she said.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1777651868
OL,3,CMan returns medieval tiles after
OL,4,Ckeeping them in biscuit tin for 59
OL,5,Cyears
OL,7,FAnd while she couldn't agree Simon had
OL,8,Fdone the curators a "favour" by taking
OL,9,Fthe tiles, she did say preserving
OL,10,Farchaeology from the elements is
OL,11,F"always a good thing".
OL,13,FDespite encouraging his son to take
OL,14,Fthe tiles back in 1967, Simon said it
OL,15,Fwas not indicative of the kind of man
OL,16,Fhis father was.
OL,18,F"He wasn't a bad bloke," he said.
OL,20,F"Apart from the fact he was an estate
OL,21,Fagent."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
